Are you up for a humorless war drama with FTL travel and androids with a strange religious explanation for everything?  Really?  What if it has shaky camerawork and awkward lighting that makes it extra hard to encode at lower bitrates?  Great!  SO SAY WE ALL.

REPACK: Corrected the episodes S03E06-S03E08 and added higher-resolution versions of the webisodes.

These copies are drawn from the highest quality sources possible, but they are encoded with lower bitrates at 360p resolution to make them ideal for the small screen - phones, tablets, laptops, and monitors.
